{
  "stem": "14613.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we've learned that, there was a short period of time that, for example, we can plant potatoes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But between the times that the potatoes will grow, we can have some-- some lettuce.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we would take the lettuce and use in a few weeks, and then the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had, by and large, more food, because this [NON-ENGLISH], this little piece of land, which was very difficult to get-- and yet we got it-- saved us both during the summer, and gave us some food for the winter.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we did work very hard for it, because you didn't have an irrigation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know my brother and myself, we had to bring water in buckets and water these plants, particularly when they were young.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then when they were growing, we had to bunch ourselves, the people had these [NON-ENGLISH], these pieces of land, and we had to watch it day and night, because the moment they started to grow, if you would not watch it, day and night, starving people would just overrun it.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so even-- even the resentment grew [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that the people that had more, there was building up of resentments against the-- against the the one that had nothing.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German presence in the ghetto, as I have seen it, was very limited, really.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by and large, we did not have-- did not not have a direct contact with the Germans, by and large.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- every now and then they would come to the ghetto, and if they came, the streets would be empty from us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so that it was not so visible in the ghetto, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] at least at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
